title: How I Got A Fake Model On Billboards Across London... For Free
description: In this video, Max Fosh explains how he managed to get a fake model on billboards across London without spending any money.
summary: Max Fosh pulls off a hilarious stunt by getting a fake model on billboards across London for free.
payoff: The payoff comes when Max reveals that he used a simple Photoshop trick to create a fake model and then submitted it to a billboard company, who unknowingly put it up on billboards across London. The absurdity of the situation and the fact that it was all done for free adds to the humor of the prank.
